Name: plonetheme.stylized
Version: 0.2
Summary: An installable theme for Plone 3.0 based on the stylized theme by NodeThirtyThree.
Home-page: http://svn.plone.org/svn/collective/
Author: Timo Stollenwerk
Author-email: timo@zmag.de
License: GPL
Description: Introduction
        ============
        
        An installable theme for Plone 3.0 based on the stylized_ theme by `NodeThirtyThree`_.
        
        .. _stylized: http://www.freecsstemplates.org/preview/stylized
        .. _`NodeThirtyThree`: http://www.nodethirtythree.com/
        
        
        
        Buildout Installation
        =====================
        
        Add the following code to your buildout.cfg::
        
        [buildout]
        ...
        eggs =
        ...
        collective.stylized
        ...
        
        ...
        [instance]
        ...
        zcml =
        ...
        collective.stylized
        ...
        
        Changelog
        =========
        
        0.2 - (2008/10/25)
        ------------------
        
        * Margin of ul/ol in #content fixed
        * Message icon fixed
        * Portal description fixed
        * Portal siteactions added
        * Color of status "published" fixed
        * Show manage portlet link when no portlets are active
        
        0.1 - (2008/10/24)
        ------------------
        
        * Initial release
        
        
